Use existing API calls.
First call AccountAPI.createCompany, which creates a brand new company : /api/account/v1/companies
Example: 

{code:java}
{
"name":"Company 2 VIA API",
"status": "ACTIVE"    <- new field, will be merged soon
}
{code}

The response will return the UUID of the company, which will be needed for the next call.

Second call AccountAPI.createCompanyUser :  /api/account/v1/companies/<uuid>/users?sendNotification=false
Important to set sendNotification=false. 
Example:

{code:java}
 {
    "email":"userviaapi-new4@apigettingstarted.com",
     "firstName":"User",
    "lastName":"Viaapi",
     "status" : "ACTIVE",
     "roles": [
     "BILLING_ADMIN"
   	]
 }
{code}

